    dc:description "FIGURES 53–62. Teuchothrips of Australia. T. kaurna 53–55: (53) head, thorax & pelta; (54) antenna; (55) tergites IX–X. T. kokatha 56–62: (56) head; (57) head & pronotum; (58) metanotum & pelta; (59) pronotum; (60) antenna; (61) metanotum; (62) pelta." ;
